title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to Using skyvector com
description:
In this how to we are going to look how you can use skyvector.com to lookup airport information which you can use in Flight Simulator 2020. We will have a look at the different documents and I will explain them when you can use them.

WARNING:
Although skyvector.com has the ability to create flight plans please don't use the tool for this purpose due to the fact that this is NOT allowed.
